data.description: Ranch Home in Calumet Township on ONE FULL ACRE! The one-acre lot which extends north to 46th Avenue can be used for recreational purposes, or perhaps for adding an additional garage.   3-bedroom home with the Primary Bedroom featuring a spacious closet and new carpet.  Large Main bathroom along with an additional one-half bathroom located off the family room.  Kitchen has a dining area featuring a Bay Window.  Located in Unincorporated Calumet Township with well and septic.
